~ start
if GameState.get_flag(GameState.Flags.ROOM1_DOOR_OPEN)
	The door is open.
elif GameState.get_flag(GameState.Flags.HAS_LEFT_ARM)
	You open the door with your left arm.
	do parent.rotate_y(-1.5)
	do GameState.set_flag(GameState.Flags.ROOM1_DOOR_OPEN, true)
else
	The door is closed, and you don't have any arms.
=> END